<div class="content" name="FAX_MESSAGE_1" uuid="353bdf06-225c-4274-b24b-d7832a196675"><p>An array of the <b>FAX_MESSAGE_1</b> data type can be passed
as an out parameter (as a byte array) in the <b>FAX_EnumMessagesEx</b> (section
